  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "2. Add sausages and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "3. Remove sausages and set aside.",
    "4. Add stew beef and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "5. Add onions and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "6. Add potatoes, beef broth, caraway seeds, salt, and pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "7. Return sausages to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "8. Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "9. Add tomatoes and stir to combine.",
    "10. Simmer for an additional 15 minutes.",
    "11. Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
